Introduction

This is an API for Smart Sleeve Application which is about cricket bowling. Player bowls and his bowling metrics are calculated via wrist band. Connected coach can check his bowling performance.

Account

POST Signup
/account/signup

Headers

Content-type
application/json | multipart/form-data
apiKey
****
role
player | coach
device_dimensions
'{"height":768,"width":1280}' [optional]

body

Sample
                      
      {
        "first_name": "Muhammad Wasif",
        "last_name": "Naeem",
        "email": "wasif@gmail.com",
        "password": "wasif"
      }
Structure
                      
      {
        first_name: <string>,
        last_name: <string>,
        email: <string>,
        password: <string>
      }

response

Sample
                  
      {
        "status": 201,
        "statusMessage": "success",
        "message": "Account verification email has been sent at 'wasif@gmail.com'",
        "response": {
          "data": {
            "_id": "5cdcf6fafca18e22e030002e",
            "first_name": "User",
            "last_name": "ABC",
            "email": "user@gmail.com",
            "account_status": "inactive"
          },
          "token": "*****",
          "role": "player" 
        }
      }
Structure
                  
      {
        status: < 201 | 401 | 500 >
        statusMessage: < 'success' | 'failure' >
        message: <string>
        response: {
          data: {
            _id: <string>,
            first_name: <string>,
            last_name: <string>,
            email: <string>,
            account_status: <string>
          },
          token: <string>,
          role: <string>
        }
      }
